==Korean==
===Adjective===
'''쓰다''' sseuda
#[[bitter]]
#:쓴 [[약]] '''bitter''' medicine
#:맛이 쓰다
#:Proverb:  몸에 좋은 약은 '''쓰다'''. (''Mome jo-eun yageun '''sseuda''''').  Medicine which is good for the body is bitter/ Healthy medicine is bitter.

===Verb===
'''쓰다''' sseuda
#to [[write]]
#: 소설을 쓰다. (''soseor-eul sseuda'') Write a novel.
#: 연필로 쓰다. (''yeonpil-lo sseuda'') Write with a pencil.
#to [[use]]
#: 컴퓨터를 쓰다. (''keompyuteo-reul sseuda'') Use a computer. 
#:돈을 많이 쓰다 (''ton-eul manhi sseuda'') Use (spend) a lot of money.
#to [[wear]] (on the head), to place on or above the head
#: 모자를 쓰다. (''moja-reul sseuda'') To wear a hat.
#: 우산을 쓰다. (''usan-eul sseuda'') To put up an umbrella. 
#to be [[accuse]]d of, to be [[suspect]]ed of 
#:강도 혐의를 쓰다 (''kangdo hyeumui-reul sseuda'') be suspected of robbery.

